data.text: Today’s Song of the Day comes from Gloria Gaynor back in 1978. Survivor Series is tonight and I thought the song fit the circumstance. There are a lot of big matches tonight and it should be a great show. Also, I’ll drop a clip of Michael Scott singing the lyrics to “Stayin’ Alive” and keeping up the pace of a heartbeat. I hope everyone has a great Sunday and a great lead-in to the Thanksgiving holiday.
